gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Jazz 115, Trail Blazers 99
gameRecap.excerpt: The Jazz defeated the Trail Blazers, 115-99. Jordan Clarkson led all scorers with 30 points (13-19 FG, 4-9 3PM) for the Jazz, while Lauri Markkanen added 21 points and nine rebounds in the victory. Deandre Ayton tallied 22 points and 10 rebounds for the Trail Blazers in the losing effort. The Jazz improve to 2-0 in West Group A play, 4-7 in the regular season, while the Trail Blazers fall to 1-1 in West Group A play, 3-7 in the regular season.
